.DT 
set_attack_everyone 
Discworld monster help 
set_attack_everyone 

Name
.SI 5
set_attack_everyone - Sets the attack everyone flag.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_attack_everyone(int flag);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
If this flag is set to true then the monster will attack literaly everyone
once a fight has started.  This is the flag set on hrun and stren in the
mended drum.  They attack everyone in sight.  Remember this flag
only holds for once a fight has started.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
set_throw_out, set_agressive
.EP
